---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
const isEs = false;
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" lang={lang}>
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-premium max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-light mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Henna By Hanazz is a professional henna artistry service based in Barcelona, Spain. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our website or services.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Booking information:</strong> name, email address, phone number, and any special requests you provide when booking a session.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> anonymized analytics via Google Analytics (with your consent only).</li>
          <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> payment details are processed by Bizum or bank transfer — we never store your financial information.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contract performance:</strong> processing your booking and sending confirmation messages.</li>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> analytics and tracking cookies (you can withdraw anytime).</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> improving our services and website experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain booking data for 2 years after your last appointment. Analytics data is retained for 14 months.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict, port, and object to the processing of your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us via WhatsApp or email.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">6. Complaints</h2>
        <p>If you believe we have not handled your data correctly, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) at <a href="https://www.aepd.es/" class="text-gold-dark underline">www.aepd.es</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">7. Updates</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
